Favorite Drinks
===============

A list of my favorite drinks, and favorite brands used to make thos drinks.

Favorite Brands
---------------

Absinthe	Leopold Brothers
Dark Rum	Kraken Black Spiced
Gin		Roku
Ginger Beer	Barritts | Goslings
Honey		Prarie Rock
Lemon Juice	Delallo
Dry Vermouth	Dolin
Sweet Vermouth	Dolin
Vodka		Kettle One
Whiskey		High West

Recipes
-------

Bee's Knees:
2 oz	Gin
3/4 oz	Lemon Juice
3/4 oz	Honey
Serve in martini glass

Dark 'n Stormy
1 oz	Dark Rum
2 oz	Ginger Beer
Serve in highball glass

Manhattan:
2 oz	Rye Whiskey
1 oz	Sweet Vermouth
3 dsh	Bitters
Serve in martini glass
Garnish w/ cherry

Negroni:
1 oz	Gin
1 oz	Sweet Vermouth
1 oz	Campari
Serve in highball glass

Old Fashioned:
2 oz	Whiskey
1 oz	Simple Syrup
3 dsh	Bittrs
Garnish w/ twisted and toasted orange or lemon peel
Serve in highball|martini glass

Sazerac:
0.5 oz	Simple Syrup
1/4 tsp	Peychaud's Bitters
1/8 tsp	Underberg Bitters
1 tsp	Water
1/4 C.	Rye Whiskey
2 tsp	Absinthe (or more?)
Garnish w/ lemon peel
Serve in highball glass

Snow White:
2 oz	Godiva White Chocolate Liquer
1 oz	Kettle One Vodka
0.5 oz	White Creme de Menthe
Serve in martini glass
